      "rationale": "CFD predictions of normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) agree with FDA experimental measurements within 12% across all five flow-speed operating points. Systematic over-prediction of 6% at low flow conditions is documented and attributed to secondary flow model limitations."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
