      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating machinery flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) selected as standard for CPB applications. Selection rationale documented in simulation plan."
